item.description:

The amazing soft-body physics you know from Rigs of Rods, now even better in CryEngine3. Anything can be built in the Beam physics system - cars, trucks, planes, boats, trains, cranes, tanks, helicopters, and even destructible map objects and crash test dummies. It's all real physics. item.title: Paintball Warfare - Epic Paintball Battle
item.description:
Paintball Warfare - Epic Paintball Battle
Make sure to subscribe for new vids EVERY WEEK! Or at least that's the idea :) http://www.youtube.com/devinsupertramp I'll be coming out with a video tomorrow on the making of this, check it out on my second channel! http://www.youtube.com/devingraham My friend Stephen Anderson wrote the music for this video! Make sure to check out Stephen's website in the link below! http://www.stephenjanderson.com And a super huge THANK YOU to my friends who helped make this video happen!!! Especially Dallin Smith, Creigton Baird, and Austin Baird. Cinematography by: Devin Graham Jace Leroy Chris McClain Color Correction by Jacob Schwarz http://www.youtube.com/jacobschwarz And a super huge thanks to my friends youtube channel, the Warialasky! Make sure to check them out! http://www.youtube.com/Warialasky This video was shot with Canon 5D Mark III, and Contour cameras. For lenses we used Canon 16-35mm F/2.8 L series lenses and Canon 70-200mm F/2.8. Almost everything was shot with an ISO of 100, and shutter of 1/4000. My friend Jace Leroy who always shoots with me put together an edit just from the Contour cameras we used. You can check that video out in this link below. http://youtu.be/fNg8RbCrMDo We had AWESOME sponsors that helped make this video happen! Without them, none of this would have. Here is how each company contributed! Nitro Circus - http://www.nitrocircus.com They hooked us up with their stunt drivers, and trophy cars!!! They were the ones they took the jump over the other car! And they let us use their property to film on! They have a full length feature film coming out soon! So check it! :) Spyder - http://www.spyder.tv/ They provided a ton of paintball guns and mask, and even technicians to help if we ran into any problems. Nelson - http://www.nelsonpaintball.com They hooked us up with 100,000 paintballs for this!!! HUGE HELP! MBS Mountain Boards - http://www.mbs.com They provided awesome mountain boarder stunt people! Guerilla Air - Gave us all the tanks of air!! http://www.guerrillaair.com Also, if you want to know more about the vechicle we used that was flying around in the sky shooting down, you can check out these two links for more info! This is a fairly brand new sport, so all the info you need is down below! http://www.parajet.com http://www.flyparamania.com And last but not least, make sure to follow me on twitter and facebook, it's the cool thing to do these days :) https://www.facebook.com/devinsupertrampyoutube http://twitter.com/devinsupertramp For business enquires ONLY, contact me here: devinsupertramp@gmail.com
